{"id":13195,"date":"2022-03-15T09:10:32","date_gmt":"2022-03-15T02:10:32","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13195"},"modified":"2022-03-15T09:10:32","modified_gmt":"2022-03-15T02:10:32","slug":"phan-khuc-xe-do-thi-co-nho-hyundai-grand-i10-cho-cac-xe-cung-phan-khuc-hit-khoi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/phan-khuc-xe-do-thi-co-nho-hyundai-grand-i10-cho-cac-xe-cung-phan-khuc-hit-khoi\/","title":{"rendered":"Ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf: Hyundai Grand i10 cho c\u00e1c xe c\u00f9ng ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac &#8216;h\u00edt kh\u00f3i&#8217;"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua doanh s\u1ed1 ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi VinFast Fadil &#8220;h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i&#8221;, \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Hyundai Grand i10 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i v\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc sang n\u0103m 2022, ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe h\u1ea1ng A gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 5 m\u1eabu xe bao g\u1ed3m: VinFast Fadil, Hyundai Grand i10, KIA Morning, Honda Brio v\u00e0 Toyota Wigo. Theo k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1eb5n, VinFast Fadil s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay do h\u00e3ng xe Vi\u1ec7t mu\u1ed1n d\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t xe \u0111i\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p>Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c mua xe VinFast Fadil. Sau m\u00e0n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u &#8220;vua doanh s\u1ed1&#8221; n\u0103m 2021, doanh s\u1ed1 Fadil b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ea3o chi\u1ec1u. Th\u00e1ng 2 v\u1eeba qua ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 697 xe VinFast Fadil ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c l\u0103n b\u00e1nh, gi\u1ea3m h\u01a1n 50% so v\u1edbi doanh s\u1ed1 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ( 1.401 xe). \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn VinFast Fadil m\u1ea5t d\u1ea5u trong Top 10 xe b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1ed1 1 ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac cho Hyundai Grand i10.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/phan-khuc-xe-do-thi-co-nho-hyundai-grand-i10-cho-cac-xe-cung-phan-khuc-hit-khoi\/phan-khuc-xe-do-thi-anh-1\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13198\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13198\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/phan-khuc-xe-do-thi-anh-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"760\" height=\"326\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/phan-khuc-xe-do-thi-anh-1.png 760w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/phan-khuc-xe-do-thi-anh-1-300x129.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p><em>Doanh s\u1ed1 ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf th\u00e1ng 2\/2022.<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Hyundai Grand i10 2022 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe duy nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng d\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi 987 xe b\u00e1n ra th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u0103ng 77 xe so v\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 1\/2022. Hyundai Grand i10 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c phong \u0111\u1ed9 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac m\u00e0 c\u00f2n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1eabu xe duy nh\u1ea5t trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch 10 xe b\u00e1n ch\u1ea1y nh\u1ea5t th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/phan-khuc-xe-do-thi-co-nho-hyundai-grand-i10-cho-cac-xe-cung-phan-khuc-hit-khoi\/hyundai-grand-i10-2021-hatchba-7025-3582-1646191323\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13197\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13197\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/hyundai-grand-i10-2021-hatchba-7025-3582-1646191323.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/hyundai-grand-i10-2021-hatchba-7025-3582-1646191323.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/hyundai-grand-i10-2021-hatchba-7025-3582-1646191323-300x192.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/hyundai-grand-i10-2021-hatchba-7025-3582-1646191323-1024x655.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/hyundai-grand-i10-2021-hatchba-7025-3582-1646191323-768x492.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>X\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 l\u00e0 KIA Morning v\u1edbi doanh s\u1ed1 401 xe, gi\u1ea3m nh\u1eb9 so v\u1edbi th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2022. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, KIA Morning l\u00e0 m\u1eabu xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mua xe ch\u1ea1y d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 nh\u1edd gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac. Th\u00e1ng 11\/2020, KIA Morning th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 th\u1ee9 4 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft v\u1edbi 2 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n g\u1ed3m X-Line v\u00e0 GT-Line gi\u00e1 439 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/p>\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap Morning t\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh, v\u1eabn trung th\u00e0nh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Honda Brio v\u00e0 Toyota Wigo l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t chia nhau hai v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi doanh s\u1ed1 298 xe v\u00e0 144 xe.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/phan-khuc-xe-do-thi-co-nho-hyundai-grand-i10-cho-cac-xe-cung-phan-khuc-hit-khoi\/gia-xe-kia-morning-2021-oto-com-vn-4-3e85\/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-13196\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13196\" src=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gia-xe-kia-morning-2021-oto-com-vn-4-3e85.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gia-xe-kia-morning-2021-oto-com-vn-4-3e85.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gia-xe-kia-morning-2021-oto-com-vn-4-3e85-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gia-xe-kia-morning-2021-oto-com-vn-4-3e85-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/03\/gia-xe-kia-morning-2021-oto-com-vn-4-3e85-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Ngu\u1ed3n: Internet<\/p>\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi b\u1edfi th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua n\u0103m 2022 c\u00f2n d\u00e0i. VinFast v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a m\u1eabu xe h\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ua m\u1edbi v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf c\u1ea1nh tranh s\u00f4i n\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p>Ngay trong th\u00e1ng 3 n\u00e0y, h\u00e3ng xe Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 10 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 kh\u00e1ch mua VinFast Fadil, m\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eeb tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c h\u1eadu m\u00e3i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Fadil s\u1ebd s\u1edbm l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua doanh s\u1ed1 ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac xe \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec3n bi\u1ebfn b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi VinFast Fadil &#8220;h\u1ee5t 